My gosh!

54
00:03:42,600 --> 00:03:44,800
Gosh, I'm sorry.

55
00:03:44,800 --> 00:03:46,280
I didn't know you were in there.

56
00:03:46,280 --> 00:03:49,180
Su Jeong, why were you in there...

57
00:03:49,180 --> 00:03:52,990
