59
00:03:55,860 --> 00:03:57,740
How about your size? Did you find any?

60
00:03:57,740 --> 00:04:00,080
- Well, no.
- Right.

61
00:04:00,080 --> 00:04:03,010
Only my size was missing.

62
00:04:03,010 --> 00:04:05,150
We can try something else, then.

63
00:04:05,150 --> 00:04:06,880
That. That one. I love that one.

64
00:04:06,880 --> 00:04:09,860
That gray one. The gray one. The gray one.

65
00:04:09,860 --> 00:04:11,910
How's the gray one? It's so pretty.

66
00:04:11,910 --> 00:04:13,190
Do you have his size?

67
00:04:13,190 --> 00:04:14,540
Would you be able to check?

68
00:04:14,540 --> 00:04:16,830
- Well, yes. Just one moment.
- O-Okay.

69
00:04:16,830 --> 00:04:18,510
