83
00:05:21,350 --> 00:05:23,250
I'm sorry.

84
00:05:26,490 --> 00:05:28,080
It's okay.

85
00:05:28,080 --> 00:05:29,940
You can get going.

86
00:05:31,140 --> 00:05:32,470
I'm sorry.

87
00:05:32,470 --> 00:05:34,450
I'm so sorry.

88
00:05:50,840 --> 00:05:52,620
So,

89
00:05:52,620 --> 00:05:55,600
