90
00:06:06,410 --> 00:06:08,800
You can't just act like this.

91
00:06:08,800 --> 00:06:10,220
I was put in a tough spot.

92
00:06:10,220 --> 00:06:11,840
I already felt bad for him.

93
00:06:11,840 --> 00:06:15,210
I don't feel bad for that man.

94
00:06:15,210 --> 00:06:17,430
- What?
- By the way,

95
00:06:17,430 --> 00:06:20,230
I'm sorry I didn't remember the kiss.

96
00:06:20,230 --> 00:06:22,140
I apologize for that.

97
00:06:23,160 --> 00:06:25,210
You're apologizing now?

98
00:06:27,410 --> 00:06:30,160
Well, fine. I'll accept it.

99
00:06:30,160 --> 00:06:33,280
I decided to think it never happened, anyway.

100
00:06:34,270 --> 00:06:35,390
Never happened?

101
00:06:35,390 --> 00:06:38,870
