102
00:06:40,740 --> 00:06:43,010
I think you're mistaken.

103
00:06:43,010 --> 00:06:45,400
I only apologized for not remembering.

104
00:06:45,400 --> 00:06:47,970
I'm not sorry I kissed you. That was...

105
00:06:50,450 --> 00:06:52,540
not a mistake.

106
00:06:58,530 --> 00:07:00,750
Well...

107
00:07:00,750 --> 00:07:04,300
