108
00:07:04,300 --> 00:07:06,400
It wasn't a mistake.

109
00:07:06,400 --> 00:07:08,820
It's not like I did it for no reason.

110
00:07:15,200 --> 00:07:17,280
[Jin unni]

111
00:07:18,370 --> 00:07:19,620
Um...

112
00:07:20,470 --> 00:07:23,390
I just remembered I'm meeting someone.

113
00:07:23,390 --> 00:07:25,990
I-I'll talk to you later.

114
00:07:25,990 --> 00:07:27,450
Wait...

115
00:07:34,450 --> 00:07:36,680
Is she shy?

116
00:07:39,090 --> 00:07:41,310
I can see that.

117
00:07:41,310 --> 00:07:43,670
She's shyer than I thought.

118
00:07:57,260 --> 00:07:59,850
Are you all burning up from the date?

119
00:07:59,850 --> 00:08:01,510
Unni!

120
00:08:01,510 --> 00:08:04,550
I was asking if your heart was feeling the passion.

121
00:08:04,550 --> 00:08:07,110
What are you thinking?

122
00:08:07,110 --> 00:08:10,650
So? Will you keep seeing him?

123
00:08:10,650 --> 00:08:13,120
No. I turned him down.

124
00:08:13,120 --> 00:08:15,990
What? Why?

125
00:08:15,990 --> 00:08:17,260
I thought he seemed all right.

126
00:08:17,260 --> 00:08:19,230
You didn't like him this time?

127
00:08:19,230 --> 00:08:21,740
He seemed all right this time, too.

128
00:08:21,740 --> 00:08:23,360
That's what I'm saying.

129
00:08:23,360 --> 00:08:25,700
He's the type you wanted.

130
00:08:25,700 --> 00:08:28,570
He's older, has a stable job,

131
00:08:28,570 --> 00:08:31,280
and has a down-to-earth taste and personality.

132
00:08:31,280 --> 00:08:32,950
Yeah.

133
00:08:32,950 --> 00:08:34,230
I don't like younger men,

134
00:08:34,230 --> 00:08:36,620
and I hate men with strange tastes, too.

135
00:08:36,620 --> 00:08:38,890
So, what's the issue?

136
00:08:41,930 --> 00:08:44,070
Do you...

137
00:08:44,070 --> 00:08:48,240
have someone else in mind, by chance?

138
00:08:50,200 --> 00:08:51,710
A highball, please.

139
00:08:51,710 --> 00:08:53,260
Okay.

140
00:08:54,420 --> 00:08:56,160
Coming.

141
00:08:57,930 --> 00:08:59,420
No.

142
00:09:00,420 --> 00:09:02,800
I like that guy?

143
00:09:04,540 --> 00:09:06,770
There's no way.

144
00:09:18,900 --> 00:09:21,100
I was wearing this.

145
00:09:23,600 --> 00:09:27,020
Is that why she found me more attractive?

146
00:09:45,630 --> 00:09:48,750
How could I forget such a precious memory?

147
00:09:48,750 --> 00:09:50,410
Don't...

148
00:09:50,410 --> 00:09:53,670
Don't ever go anywhere near makgeolli, Ban Ju Yeon.

149
00:10:30,330 --> 00:10:32,560
[Music for sleeping]

150
00:10:40,390 --> 00:10:41,920
It wasn't a mistake.

151
00:10:41,920 --> 00:10:44,640
It's not like I did it for no reason.

152
00:10:44,640 --> 00:10:47,100
What now, then?

153
00:10:47,100 --> 00:10:49,400
Does he want to go out or something?

154
00:10:50,290 --> 00:10:54,100
He's the same age as Su Bin. The same age.

155
00:10:57,720 --> 00:11:00,780
[Director Ban Ju Yeon]

156
00:11:06,450 --> 00:11:08,020
[He Kisses for 6,000 Won]

157
00:11:13,360 --> 00:11:15,400
I'm not like this guy.

158
00:11:15,400 --> 00:11:18,010
What's he talking about?

159
00:11:19,060 --> 00:11:21,480
He's so funny.

160
00:11:21,480 --> 00:11:23,970
Please believe me.

161
00:11:23,970 --> 00:11:25,910
What's he saying?

162
00:11:29,880 --> 00:11:31,890
What's this?

163
00:11:42,440 --> 00:11:45,280
Gosh, I don't know!

164
00:11:47,100 --> 00:11:49,380
