165
00:11:49,380 --> 00:11:51,400
When is "later," exactly?

166
00:12:05,880 --> 00:12:07,620
[Team Leader Baek Su Jeong]

167
00:12:08,590 --> 00:12:10,900
It's too formal.

168
00:12:10,900 --> 00:12:15,120
Still...
[Ban Ju Yeon / Baek Su Jeong]

169
00:12:15,120 --> 00:12:17,150
we kissed once.

170
00:12:20,540 --> 00:12:22,800
[Friend info]

171
00:12:22,800 --> 00:12:24,720
[Friend info: Ms. Baek Su Jeong]

172
00:12:27,140 --> 00:12:34,150
[Friend info: Su Jeong]

173
00:12:39,050 --> 00:12:41,140
Sometimes you have to wait.

174
00:12:41,140 --> 00:12:42,740
I'll see her tomorrow.

175
00:12:42,740 --> 00:12:44,960
Let's not be hasty.

176
00:12:54,090 --> 00:12:55,780
Su Jeong.

177
00:12:57,140 --> 00:13:00,580
I heard your friend rejected that man.

178
00:13:00,580 --> 00:13:02,440
Yes. How did you know?

179
00:13:02,440 --> 00:13:05,820
Hey, his mom is apparently crying about it

180
00:13:05,820 --> 00:13:08,380
