181
00:13:08,380 --> 00:13:12,590
Geez! I told you to go on a date instead.

182
00:13:12,590 --> 00:13:15,970
Not many men are okay with a flawed woman.

183
00:13:15,970 --> 00:13:17,610
Hold on.

184
00:13:17,610 --> 00:13:19,000
Am I the flawed woman?

185
00:13:19,000 --> 00:13:21,200
That's right. Why did you have to get divorced?

186
00:13:21,200 --> 00:13:23,880
Why is getting divorced a flaw?

187
00:13:23,880 --> 00:13:26,860
I mean, you couldn't control your temper

188
00:13:26,860 --> 00:13:28,520
