189
00:13:28,520 --> 00:13:31,230
You can't do that in the right mind.

190
00:13:31,230 --> 00:13:33,760
That's how bad it was for me.

191
00:13:33,760 --> 00:13:35,200
Anyway, I'm fine hearing that

192
00:13:35,200 --> 00:13:36,890
