195
00:13:40,680 --> 00:13:42,670
I'm not the only one who says that.

196
00:13:42,670 --> 00:13:44,800
Everyone thinks you're flawed.

197
00:13:44,800 --> 00:13:46,970
- A lot of people don't.
- Aigoo...

198
00:13:46,970 --> 00:13:48,520
It's just you. Just you.

199
00:13:48,520 --> 00:13:51,270
I'm serious. There's someone else.

200
00:13:52,100 --> 00:13:53,620
Is it a man?

201
00:13:53,620 --> 00:13:55,110
Seriously.

202
00:13:55,110 --> 00:13:58,030
You can't stop thinking about men, can you?

203
00:13:58,030 --> 00:14:00,500
Let me meet him if it's a man.

204
00:14:00,500 --> 00:14:02,590
Why? Will you date him?

205
00:14:02,590 --> 00:14:04,700
Aigoo, aigoo, you little.

206
00:14:04,700 --> 00:14:06,500
You're a little brat, aren't you?

207
00:14:06,500 --> 00:14:09,520
Dad, Mom wants to date other men.

208
00:14:09,520 --> 00:14:12,020
Hey, Seo Ha Jin,

209
00:14:12,020 --> 00:14:13,610
