210
00:14:13,610 --> 00:14:16,040
It's because she worries about you.

211
00:14:16,040 --> 00:14:19,690
Aigoo, poor me for being single.

212
00:14:38,630 --> 00:14:41,530
Are you looking for someone?

213
00:14:43,580 --> 00:14:45,290
I assure you I'm not.

214
00:14:45,290 --> 00:14:48,260
Let's go up. We have lots of important things to do.

215
00:14:59,070 --> 00:15:00,570
Seok Hui,

216
00:15:00,570 --> 00:15:02,400
