217
00:15:02,400 --> 00:15:03,960
Because it's my job.

218
00:15:03,960 --> 00:15:05,590
I know, but give them to me.

219
00:15:05,590 --> 00:15:06,720
- I'll carry them.
- I'm okay.

220
00:15:06,720 --> 00:15:08,250
No.

221
00:15:10,540 --> 00:15:12,040
Well...

222
00:15:21,600 --> 00:15:23,280
- Hello.
- Hello.

223
00:15:23,280 --> 00:15:25,500
Hello.

224
00:15:25,500 --> 00:15:27,110
Hello.

225
00:15:29,830 --> 00:15:32,860
Team Leader, aren't you getting in?

226
00:15:43,530 --> 00:15:44,620
- Team Leader Baek-
- Deputy Jeong.

227
00:15:44,620 --> 00:15:45,490
Yes.

228
00:15:45,490 --> 00:15:48,710
Are Ludwig, Frid, Heinrich, Carlos, and Barbarossa doing well?

229
00:15:48,710 --> 00:15:50,820
How do you know my dogs' names?

230
00:15:50,820 --> 00:15:52,350
Even my parents don't know.

231
00:15:52,350 --> 00:15:53,940
Of course I do.

232
00:15:53,940 --> 00:15:56,120
I heard you rescued them.

233
00:15:56,120 --> 00:15:59,680
I've always admired your kindness.

234
00:16:00,480 --> 00:16:02,270
I'm so touched.

235
00:16:16,900 --> 00:16:18,660
What the heck?

236
00:16:27,520 --> 00:16:29,120
Na Na, eat this.

237
00:16:29,120 --> 00:16:31,490
- I'll eat out.
- What?

238
00:16:33,420 --> 00:16:35,660
Why does she keep avoiding me?

239
00:16:47,880 --> 00:16:50,430
[I am the devil]

240
00:16:50,430 --> 00:16:53,000
[Pros / Cons]

241
00:16:53,000 --> 00:16:54,760
[Pros: None / Cons: Too young, bad style...]

242
00:16:54,760 --> 00:16:56,300
[Pros: None / Cons: Dragon tattoo...]

243
00:16:56,300 --> 00:16:58,500
It's all stuff like this?

244
00:16:58,500 --> 00:17:01,500
[A lightweight (terrible memory), music hurts ears...]

