00:17:09,080 --> 00:17:11,360
[No. 1 Hardware]

246
00:17:19,720 --> 00:17:21,520
Gosh, I'm dying.

247
00:17:28,090 --> 00:17:31,780
Yongsung Department Store put forward Director Ban,

248
00:17:31,780 --> 00:17:33,650
