256
00:18:14,290 --> 00:18:16,220
Team Leader, the promotional article is up.

257
00:18:16,220 --> 00:18:17,550
I'll send you the link.

258
00:18:17,550 --> 00:18:19,400
Okay. I'll check it right away.

259
00:18:19,400 --> 00:18:22,340
