264
00:18:37,520 --> 00:18:38,580
[Yongsung = Silver spoon]

265
00:18:38,580 --> 00:18:39,620
[I'm jealous of the Yongsung employees]

266
00:18:41,460 --> 00:18:43,200
I know.

267
00:18:44,210 --> 00:18:46,990
