268
00:18:49,050 --> 00:18:51,800
I had no reason to ponder.

269
00:18:58,580 --> 00:19:00,370
[I am the devil]

270
00:19:00,370 --> 00:19:02,500
[Trash]

271
00:19:25,140 --> 00:19:28,560
I have no reason to avoid him. Why am I doing this?

272
00:19:30,430 --> 00:19:32,370
I know.

273
00:19:32,370 --> 00:19:34,970
It's not like you can keep doing this.

274
00:19:36,860 --> 00:19:39,090
We were supposed to talk. Why keep avoiding me?

275
00:19:39,090 --> 00:19:42,230
You're friendly to everyone else.

276
00:19:43,280 --> 00:19:44,660
What did you want to talk about?

277
00:19:44,660 --> 00:19:46,120
I told you.

278
00:19:46,120 --> 00:19:49,820
