00:37:35,650 --> 00:37:38,900
[2024 Future Energy Industry Expo]

558
00:37:39,860 --> 00:37:41,670
Chairwoman.

559
00:37:42,670 --> 00:37:43,980
Hello.

560
00:37:43,980 --> 00:37:45,860
You remember me, right? I'm Sin Won.

561
00:37:45,860 --> 00:37:47,090
Kim Sin Won.

562
00:37:47,090 --> 00:37:48,820
Yes.

563
00:37:48,820 --> 00:37:50,690
Long time no see.

564
00:37:50,690 --> 00:37:54,300
I heard you're still close with Director Ban.

565
00:37:54,300 --> 00:37:55,760
Yes, of course.

566
00:37:55,760 --> 00:37:57,620
We're basically like brothers.

567
00:37:57,620 --> 00:37:59,840
Since he's working at the department store,

568
00:37:59,840 --> 00:38:01,930
we're able to hang out more often.

569
00:38:01,930 --> 00:38:03,370
Is that so?

570
00:38:03,370 --> 00:38:07,880
By the way, you haven't changed at all.

571
00:38:07,880 --> 00:38:10,040
Does the passage of time not apply to you?

572
00:38:10,040 --> 00:38:13,010
The PR Team at the HQ needs to work harder.

573
00:38:13,010 --> 00:38:15,040
Your photos don't do justice.

574
00:38:15,040 --> 00:38:17,530
You look so young and beautiful.

575
00:38:19,320 --> 00:38:22,460
You're still good at schmoozing.

576
00:38:22,460 --> 00:38:23,800
Thank you.

577
00:38:23,800 --> 00:38:26,880
By the way, what brings you here?

578
00:38:26,880 --> 00:38:30,050
Oh, well, I-I was just in the area.

579
00:38:30,050 --> 00:38:32,000
Have you eaten, Chairwoman?

580
00:38:32,000 --> 00:38:34,480
If you haven't, would you like to join me?

581
00:38:34,480 --> 00:38:35,960
When would I ever get to

582
00:38:35,960 --> 00:38:39,310
have the honor of having a meal with you again?

583
00:38:39,310 --> 00:38:40,650
Yes.

584
00:38:40,650 --> 00:38:42,380
I'm sorry,

585
00:38:42,380 --> 00:38:44,510
but I need to get going. I'm busy.

586
00:38:44,510 --> 00:38:46,250
Chairwoman.

587
00:38:46,250 --> 00:38:49,560
How about a t-tea for a moment, then?

588
00:38:49,560 --> 00:38:52,700
Stop taking more of my time.

589
00:38:54,480 --> 00:38:56,500
T-Take care.

590
00:39:00,810 --> 00:39:02,280
[Bbanjju]

591
00:39:03,820 --> 00:39:06,450
Yes, I did try to stall her

592
00:39:06,450 --> 00:39:08,270
but I think eating with her is pushing it.

593
00:39:08,270 --> 00:39:10,530
What's going on, exactly?

594
00:39:10,530 --> 00:39:11,980
If you leave your truck here,

595
00:39:11,980 --> 00:39:14,290
how about the other cars?

596
00:39:14,290 --> 00:39:16,070
Restroom?

597
00:39:17,470 --> 00:39:20,150
I'll call the police if you don't come now.

598
00:39:20,150 --> 00:39:22,040
A lot of time has passed.

599
00:39:22,040 --> 00:39:25,440
Should I postpone the visit to the Director's house?

600
00:39:25,440 --> 00:39:26,830
It's okay.

601
00:39:27,460 --> 00:39:29,400
It'd just take a moment, anyway.

602
00:39:29,400 --> 00:39:30,820
You have another appointment afterward, too.

603
00:39:30,820 --> 00:39:33,120
Why are we still talking?

604
00:39:33,910 --> 00:39:35,830
I'm sorry.

605
00:39:40,620 --> 00:39:43,380
I'm sorry, I was in such a hurry.

606
00:39:43,380 --> 00:39:47,050
I think a car could easily pass through here.

607
00:39:47,050 --> 00:39:48,420
How weird.

608
00:39:48,420 --> 00:39:51,770
What do you mean, parked in the middle of the road?

609
00:39:51,770 --> 00:39:53,190
Did I?

610
00:39:53,190 --> 00:39:55,550
But I guess you can't...

611
00:39:55,550 --> 00:39:57,500
you can't just go like this.

612
00:39:57,500 --> 00:39:59,830
Whatever. Move your truck now.

613
00:39:59,830 --> 00:40:01,140
Okay, okay.

614
00:40:01,140 --> 00:40:03,690
I feel so terrible, by the way.

615
00:40:03,690 --> 00:40:05,780
Should I cut some sashimi for you?

616
00:40:06,450 --> 00:40:08,870
I have a ton of fish straight from Jeju-

617
00:40:08,870 --> 00:40:12,690
Look! Stop talking nonsense and move the truck!

618
00:40:13,820 --> 00:40:15,310
I guess you don't want it.

619
00:40:15,310 --> 00:40:17,570
I got it! Okay.

620
00:40:34,260 --> 00:40:35,690
Yes, Su Jeong.

621
00:40:35,690 --> 00:40:38,210
I did my best, but...

622
00:40:38,210 --> 00:40:41,160
So, why are you trying to stop the Chairwoman?

623
00:41:06,850 --> 00:41:09,560
You'll tell me later?

624
00:41:10,560 --> 00:41:12,520
Huh? Okay.

625
00:41:12,520 --> 00:41:15,010
Hello? Hello...

626
00:41:15,860 --> 00:41:17,400
What?

627
00:41:20,640 --> 00:41:22,950
I can't believe I ran into you here.

628
00:41:24,800 --> 00:41:27,410
I know. What brings you here?

629
00:41:27,410 --> 00:41:29,990
Su Jeong asked me a favor.

630
00:41:29,990 --> 00:41:32,710
Huh? Ju Yeon asked me a favor.

631
00:41:32,710 --> 00:41:34,080
Really?

632
00:41:34,080 --> 00:41:36,090
I thought they weren't close anymore.

633
00:41:36,090 --> 00:41:37,760
Was I wrong?

634
00:41:39,350 --> 00:41:40,980
Anyway, good to see you.

635
00:41:40,980 --> 00:41:42,430
I'll get going now.

636
00:41:42,430 --> 00:41:43,860
Okay.

637
00:41:44,680 --> 00:41:46,930
- Drive safely.
- Okay.

638
00:41:59,310 --> 00:42:01,820
If she was so happy to see me,

639
00:42:01,820 --> 00:42:03,970
she should've gotten out briefly.

640
00:42:25,500 --> 00:42:28,090
What are you doing? Load the rest of the stuff.

641
00:42:28,090 --> 00:42:30,570
Yes, I should.

642
00:42:35,310 --> 00:42:37,510
We're at the parking lot.

643
00:42:37,510 --> 00:42:39,970
They're in front of the building now.

644
00:42:41,010 --> 00:42:42,480
Already?

645
00:42:43,240 --> 00:42:45,540
We moved the important stuff, right?

646
00:42:45,540 --> 00:42:47,490
What should we do with the rest?

647
00:42:47,490 --> 00:42:49,040
If we blocked the door to this room-

648
00:42:49,040 --> 00:42:50,750
She's already suspicious.

649
00:42:50,750 --> 00:42:52,620
She won't just go back.

650
00:42:52,620 --> 00:42:54,630
What should we do, then?

651
00:43:17,950 --> 00:43:21,580
I came to see how you live.

652
00:43:21,580 --> 00:43:23,480
I guess you were about to leave.

653
00:43:23,480 --> 00:43:24,950
Yes.

654
00:43:24,950 --> 00:43:27,390
I'd like to invite you next time if that's okay-

655
00:43:27,390 --> 00:43:30,740
No need to be invited to check out your place.

656
00:43:30,740 --> 00:43:32,180
Why?

657
00:43:32,180 --> 00:43:35,580
Is there a reason I shouldn't go into your place?

658
00:43:39,620 --> 00:43:41,470
No.

659
00:43:41,470 --> 00:43:45,050
Let's go up together if it's not anything urgent.

660
00:44:03,490 --> 00:44:05,860
Take me to the study.

661
00:44:05,860 --> 00:44:07,360
Okay.

662
00:44:40,120 --> 00:44:42,620
It looks normal.

663
00:44:43,810 --> 00:44:47,700
I'm curious why you don't let her clean this room.

664
00:44:54,030 --> 00:44:56,110
Are you...

665
00:44:56,110 --> 00:44:59,560
hiding something in here?

666
00:45:00,690 --> 00:45:02,130
Huh?

667
00:45:30,190 --> 00:45:32,020
I'm sorry.

668
00:45:34,790 --> 00:45:36,390
I'll leave first.

669
00:45:36,390 --> 00:45:39,580
You don't want to leave now and run into her.

670
00:45:43,490 --> 00:45:45,160
Stay here.

671
00:46:01,270 --> 00:46:04,560
I thought you were doing something silly again.

672
00:46:04,560 --> 00:46:07,180
Were you trying to hide this?

673
00:46:08,560 --> 00:46:11,220
I know you wouldn't be happy

674
00:46:12,220 --> 00:46:14,390
if you knew I had that photo.

675
00:46:16,840 --> 00:46:18,940
I don't have the right to

676
00:46:20,790 --> 00:46:23,310
cry or feel sad.

677
00:46:24,320 --> 00:46:25,520
Yes.

678
00:46:26,140 --> 00:46:27,940
So, why did you keep it if you knew that?

679
00:46:27,940 --> 00:46:29,520
I know...

680
00:46:32,680 --> 00:46:34,740
I don't have the right,

681
00:46:35,490 --> 00:46:38,600
but I wanted to keep a photo, at least.

682
00:46:43,070 --> 00:46:45,460
Because I miss them so much.

683
00:46:46,460 --> 00:46:49,740
You think you have the right to miss them?

684
00:46:57,410 --> 00:46:59,590
If it wasn't for you,

685
00:47:00,480 --> 00:47:03,730
my son would still be here.

686
00:47:06,920 --> 00:47:08,910
Not this stupid photo,

687
00:47:08,910 --> 00:47:11,570
but my actual son!

688
00:47:33,700 --> 00:47:35,790
Weak bastard.

689
00:48:01,880 --> 00:48:05,820
Keep a closer eye on him from now on.

690
00:48:05,820 --> 00:48:07,830
Should I have someone watch him?

691
00:48:08,480 --> 00:48:10,880
I'm having you watch him.

692
00:48:10,880 --> 00:48:13,080
Who else do we need?

693
00:48:14,080 --> 00:48:17,520
Yes, I'll watch him more closely.

694
00:48:45,360 --> 00:48:47,890
Be careful. You'll hurt yourself.

695
00:48:58,520 --> 00:49:01,930
You know my parents died in a car accident, right?

696
00:49:05,540 --> 00:49:08,980
We were on the way to an anime event.

697
00:49:08,980 --> 00:49:11,220
They were both busy,

698
00:49:12,550 --> 00:49:16,060
but I begged them because I wanted to go.

699
00:49:17,450 --> 00:49:19,850
That's when we got into an accident on the way.

700
00:49:21,310 --> 00:49:24,180
Thanks to their protection, I survived.

701
00:49:25,050 --> 00:49:26,690
But they died in an accident

702
00:49:26,690 --> 00:49:29,050
they shouldn't have been in because of me.

703
00:49:30,400 --> 00:49:34,470
Grandmother indeed lost her only son because of me.

704
00:49:35,600 --> 00:49:38,660
So, I decided to make it up for her.

705
00:49:41,100 --> 00:49:44,860
To become the person she wants and replace Father.

706
00:49:46,990 --> 00:49:48,840
Director.

707
00:49:57,510 --> 00:49:59,730
But even after that,

708
00:50:00,940 --> 00:50:03,960
I still couldn't give up on my joy.

709
00:50:03,960 --> 00:50:06,750
The next volume of my favorite cartoon,

710
00:50:06,750 --> 00:50:09,740
and the band's new song and show.

711
00:50:11,420 --> 00:50:13,790
I needed things like that

712
00:50:15,460 --> 00:50:18,120
to look forward to tomorrow.

713
00:50:22,650 --> 00:50:26,850
Even though no one loved me, I felt fulfilled.

714
00:50:31,750 --> 00:50:33,540
That's why...

715
00:50:35,730 --> 00:50:39,640
when you told me to like the things I like

716
00:50:39,640 --> 00:50:43,600
all I want in front of the fountain,

717
00:50:46,990 --> 00:50:49,390
I was really happy.

718
00:50:51,750 --> 00:50:54,060
I meant it.

719
00:50:55,080 --> 00:50:56,710
You looked...

720
00:50:58,450 --> 00:51:01,370
really happy, then.

721
00:51:03,370 --> 00:51:06,980
I wanted you to continue to be happy.

722
00:51:17,330 --> 00:51:19,090
I like you.

723
00:51:22,930 --> 00:51:26,410
I've hidden things I liked for a long time.

724
00:51:27,610 --> 00:51:30,210
Because everything I liked was a secret.

725
00:51:30,210 --> 00:51:33,220
That's why I couldn't tell you, but...

726
00:51:37,590 --> 00:51:40,460
But I like you so much, Baek Su Jeong.

727
00:51:46,860 --> 00:51:49,190
I'm sorry I couldn't hold it in.

728
00:51:52,110 --> 00:51:54,250
Thank you for today.

729
00:52:37,120 --> 00:52:38,230
There's my daughter.

730
00:52:38,230 --> 00:52:40,430
Yes, Dad. You were home.

731
00:52:40,430 --> 00:52:41,800
What are you talking about?

732
00:52:41,800 --> 00:52:43,540
You asked me to receive packages.

733
00:52:43,540 --> 00:52:46,110
People came to deliver them and left.

734
00:52:46,110 --> 00:52:48,940
Oh, yeah. That's right.

735
00:52:48,940 --> 00:52:50,270
Are you sick?

736
00:52:50,270 --> 00:52:52,670
You were meeting someone. You look terrible.

737
00:52:52,670 --> 00:52:55,190
No, I'm not sick.

738
00:52:55,190 --> 00:52:58,040
I asked them to put the packages in the attic.

739
00:52:58,040 --> 00:53:00,360
Why was there so much stuff?

740
00:53:01,070 --> 00:53:02,890
Someone I know asked me to keep them briefly.

741
00:53:02,890 --> 00:53:04,490
They'll take them back soon.

742
00:53:04,490 --> 00:53:06,870
We don't use that space, anyway.

743
00:53:06,870 --> 00:53:10,380
I don't mind keeping them there for a long time, but

744
00:53:10,380 --> 00:53:12,830
you're sure you're okay, right?

745
00:53:12,830 --> 00:53:16,660
Of course. Why would I not be okay?

746
00:53:19,980 --> 00:53:21,670
Su Jeong.

747
00:53:21,670 --> 00:53:22,940
Yes?

748
00:53:22,940 --> 00:53:24,770
You know...

749
00:53:25,570 --> 00:53:28,520
seeing you smile like that breaks my heart.

750
00:53:28,520 --> 00:53:30,590
Because I'm not good enough,

751
00:53:30,590 --> 00:53:34,020
and because you can't rely on me...

752
00:53:34,020 --> 00:53:36,860
Since you can't tell me when something's going on,

753
00:53:36,860 --> 00:53:39,530
I wonder if all you do is smile like that.

754
00:53:39,530 --> 00:53:41,220
So...

755
00:53:42,540 --> 00:53:44,180
Dad,

756
00:53:44,180 --> 00:53:47,270
please don't worry. Nothing's going on.

757
00:53:47,270 --> 00:53:50,950
I'm just tired because I've been out a while.

758
00:53:51,770 --> 00:53:54,350
Okay, then. Go inside and rest.

759
00:53:55,060 --> 00:53:56,270
You go in, too.

760
00:53:56,270 --> 00:53:57,630
Okay.

761
00:54:14,370 --> 00:54:16,980
You've been smiling a lot.

762
00:54:16,980 --> 00:54:19,030
You don't usually smile.

763
00:54:19,030 --> 00:54:21,530
How can I make you feel better?

764
00:54:23,730 --> 00:54:26,810
Isn't working alone hard?

765
00:54:26,810 --> 00:54:28,540
It's lonely, too.

766
00:54:41,190 --> 00:54:43,960
I've hidden things I liked for a long time.

767
00:54:43,960 --> 00:54:46,780
Because everything I liked was a secret.

768
00:54:46,780 --> 00:54:49,590
That's why I couldn't tell you, but...

769
00:54:50,590 --> 00:54:53,560
But I like you so much, Baek Su Jeong.

770
00:55:16,650 --> 00:55:25,120
♫ Love is just like miracle ♫

771
00:55:25,120 --> 00:55:31,750
♫ It seems close to grasp, but I can't ♫

772
00:55:31,750 --> 00:55:38,160
♫ Even if our hearts touch each other's ♫

773
00:55:38,160 --> 00:55:40,720
I know this is crazy, too, but

774
00:55:40,720 --> 00:55:42,690
I remember everything.

775
00:55:43,780 --> 00:55:45,370
That was...

776
00:55:46,840 --> 00:55:48,760
my first kiss.

777
00:55:48,760 --> 00:55:52,700
♫ The beautiful moments that passed by ♫

778
00:55:52,700 --> 00:55:56,380
♫ Can't be grasped like it was a dream ♫

779
00:55:56,380 --> 00:56:00,970
♫ We thought we were meant to be together ♫

780
00:56:00,970 --> 00:56:04,170
♫ meant to be together ♫

781
00:56:04,170 --> 00:56:08,710
♫ As much as I thought of you ♫

782
00:56:08,710 --> 00:56:10,700
The phone is powered off.

783
00:56:10,700 --> 00:56:12,990
You'll be connected to the voicemail...

784
00:56:12,990 --> 00:56:16,850
♫ I'll say it tonight ♫

785
00:56:16,850 --> 00:56:18,710
I like you.

786
00:56:20,720 --> 00:56:26,430
♫ Even if moments I hoped for come ♫

787
00:56:26,430 --> 00:56:30,420
♫ We're not each other's miracle ♫

788
00:56:30,420 --> 00:56:31,920
Director.

789
00:56:32,740 --> 00:56:34,940
Director, are you in there?

790
00:56:34,940 --> 00:56:37,690
I want to ask you something.

791
00:56:38,910 --> 00:56:43,010
♫ In the end of the faint moments ♫

792
00:56:43,010 --> 00:56:46,670
♫ You're becoming more prominent ♫

793
00:56:46,670 --> 00:56:51,510
♫ We'll meet each other again someday ♫

794
00:56:51,510 --> 00:56:54,550
♫ I'll be hoping for that ♫

795
00:56:54,550 --> 00:56:58,340
♫ As much as I've waited ♫

796
00:56:58,340 --> 00:57:03,180
♫ I hope we run into each other again ♫

797
00:57:03,180 --> 00:57:06,930
♫ I'll say it tonight ♫

798
00:57:06,930 --> 00:57:11,820
♫ I hope you'd be my miracle ♫

799
00:57:35,620 --> 00:57:37,920
There you are.

800
00:57:40,900 --> 00:57:42,740
Ms. Baek.

801
00:57:43,540 --> 00:57:46,080
I was curious about something.

802
00:57:46,790 --> 00:57:48,910
That's why I came.

803
00:57:51,260 --> 00:57:55,580
When you remembered you kissed me,

804
00:57:56,580 --> 00:57:59,430
why did you run all the way here?

805
00:58:00,630 --> 00:58:03,570
You knew it was a crazy thing to do.

806
00:58:04,470 --> 00:58:07,390
If you came looking like that, the things you hid...

807
00:58:08,570 --> 00:58:11,040
the secrets you've worked hard to keep

808
00:58:11,040 --> 00:58:14,890
could've been revealed. You knew that.

809
00:58:14,890 --> 00:58:17,170
So, why did you come?

810
00:58:21,220 --> 00:58:24,000
Just because you like me?

811
00:58:24,000 --> 00:58:26,240
For that one reason?

812
00:58:33,890 --> 00:58:35,980
Would you be okay?

813
00:58:37,350 --> 00:58:40,470
Our relationship could get exposed anytime

814
00:58:40,470 --> 00:58:43,390
and it could be problematic for your dream of

815
00:58:43,390 --> 00:58:45,550
becoming Yongsung's successor.

816
00:58:47,510 --> 00:58:49,110
I...

817
00:58:51,480 --> 00:58:54,440
think I'd be okay

818
00:58:54,440 --> 00:58:56,810
as long as I have you.

819
00:58:58,300 --> 00:59:00,990
As long as you like me.

820
00:59:12,420 --> 00:59:14,360
All right.

821
00:59:16,450 --> 00:59:18,110
If so,

822
00:59:21,070 --> 00:59:24,900
I'll become your biggest secret.

823
00:59:25,820 --> 00:59:28,950
You said everything you like is a secret.

824
00:59:31,040 --> 00:59:34,380
That means I like you, too.

